  "short_description": "Vagrant Fury is a casual arcade shooter inspired by the 80's and 90's, with a powered up soundtrack and visual style. It's like a weekend afternoon action movie: full of explosions and psycho villains, but laid back at the same time. Try to spot all the movie references!",
